caption:
Choss wrangling in Hyalite Canyon,  MT. Short and steep following the crack to the right of thin chance. "Solar Flare" Loose andesite rock eats ropes. Thanks to the people that joined in. @joshuagarrigues camera of the hold snapping at the chains.

The route will continue with low angle on low percentage holds climbing to the top. The mini gym belay ends at the lip.  #iceclimbing

